      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TORO CHASE (7) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in four of five starts to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Will be better for that first-up hit-out and gets in well at the weights with the claim. Rates the testing material. DELICIOUS DEREK (5) has been plying his trade in harder Sydney metro contests and will find this assignment much more to his liking. Respect from the champion Waller yard. FUNHOUSE (2) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and any push in betting must be noted. RALOS STAR (4) was a touch disappointing last time out but the three runs prior to start the campaign were good enough for a race of this nature. In the mix. THE AVIATOR (6) next in line from the inside alley.",
